data.name: QueryCosteos
data.value:
select Sum(QTY) Suma from (SELECT count(1) as QTY FROM [@SCGD_VEHICULO] WITH (nolock) WHERE (U_Cod_Unid = '{0}') AND (U_SALINID <> 0) AND (U_SALINID IS NOT NULL) UNION all SELECT count(1) FROM [@SCGD_VEHICULO] AS [@SCGD_VEHICULO_1] WITH (nolock) WHERE (U_Cod_Unid = '{0}') AND (U_SALINIC <> 0) AND (U_SALINIC IS NOT NULL) Union all SELECT Count(1) FROM JDT1 AS JDT1_1 WITH (nolock) INNER JOIN OJDT AS OJDT_1 WITH (nolock) ON JDT1_1.TransId = OJDT_1.TransId LEFT OUTER JOIN ORTT AS ORTT_1 WITH (nolock) ON OJDT_1.RefDate = ORTT_1.RateDate AND (ORTT_1.Currency = JDT1_1.FCCurrency OR (JDT1_1.FCCurrency IS NULL OR JDT1_1.FCCurrency = '{3}') AND ORTT_1.Currency = '{1}') WHERE (JDT1_1.U_SCGD_Cod_Unidad = '{0}') AND (JDT1_1.SYSDeb <> 0) AND (OJDT_1.TransId NOT IN (SELECT L.U_NoAsient FROM [@SCGD_GRLINES] AS L WITH (nolock) INNER JOIN [@SCGD_GOODRECEIVE] AS GR WITH (nolock) ON GR.DocEntry = L.DocEntry AND GR.U_Unidad = '{0}' AND L.U_NoAsient IS NOT NULL)) AND (OJDT_1.RefDate <= '{4}') AND (JDT1_1.U_SCGD_Cod_Tran IN (SELECT Code FROM [@SCGD_TRAN_COMP] AS [@SCGD_TRAN_COMP_7])) OR (JDT1_1.U_SCGD_Cod_Unidad = '{0}') AND (OJDT_1.TransId NOT IN (SELECT L.U_NoAsient FROM [@SCGD_GRLINES] AS L WITH (nolock) INNER JOIN [@SCGD_GOODRECEIVE] AS GR WITH (nolock) ON GR.DocEntry = L.DocEntry AND GR.U_Unidad = '{0}' AND L.U_NoAsient IS NOT NULL)) AND (OJDT_1.RefDate <= '{4}') AND (JDT1_1.U_SCGD_Cod_Tran IN (SELECT Code FROM [@SCGD_TRAN_COMP] AS [@SCGD_TRAN_COMP_5])) AND (JDT1_1.FCDebit <> 0) OR (JDT1_1.U_SCGD_Cod_Unidad = '{0}') AND (OJDT_1.TransId NOT IN (SELECT L.U_NoAsient FROM [@SCGD_GRLINES] AS L WITH (nolock) INNER JOIN [@SCGD_GOODRECEIVE] AS GR WITH (nolock) ON GR.DocEntry = L.DocEntry AND GR.U_Unidad = '{0}' AND L.U_NoAsient IS NOT NULL)) AND (OJDT_1.RefDate <= '{4}') AND (JDT1_1.U_SCGD_Cod_Tran IN (SELECT Code FROM [@SCGD_TRAN_COMP] AS [@SCGD_TRAN_COMP_4])) AND (JDT1_1.Debit <> 0) UNION all SELECT count(1) FROM JDT1 AS JDT1 WITH (nolock) INNER JOIN OJDT AS OJDT WITH (nolock) ON JDT1.TransId = OJDT.TransId LEFT OUTER JOIN ORTT AS ORTT WITH (nolock) ON OJDT.RefDate = ORTT.RateDate AND (ORTT.Currency = JDT1.FCCurrency OR (JDT1.FCCurrency IS NULL OR JDT1.FCCurrency = '{2}') AND ORTT.Currency = '{1}') WHERE (JDT1.U_SCGD_Cod_Unidad = '{0}') AND (JDT1.SYSCred <> 0) AND (OJDT.TransId NOT IN (SELECT L.U_NoAsient FROM [@SCGD_GRLINES] AS L WITH (nolock) INNER JOIN [@SCGD_GOODRECEIVE] AS GR WITH (nolock) ON GR.DocEntry = L.DocEntry AND GR.U_Unidad = '{0}' AND L.U_NoAsient IS NOT NULL)) AND (OJDT.RefDate <= '{4}') AND (JDT1.U_SCGD_Cod_Tran IN (SELECT Code FROM [@SCGD_TRAN_COMP] AS [@SCGD_TRAN_COMP_3])) OR (JDT1.U_SCGD_Cod_Unidad = '{0}') AND (OJDT.TransId NOT IN (SELECT L.U_NoAsient FROM [@SCGD_GRLINES] AS L WITH (nolock) INNER JOIN [@SCGD_GOODRECEIVE] AS GR WITH (nolock) ON GR.DocEntry = L.DocEntry AND GR.U_Unidad = '{0}' AND L.U_NoAsient IS NOT NULL)) AND (OJDT.RefDate <= '{4}') AND (JDT1.U_SCGD_Cod_Tran IN (SELECT Code FROM [@SCGD_TRAN_COMP] AS [@SCGD_TRAN_COMP_2])) AND (JDT1.FCCredit <> 0) OR (JDT1.U_SCGD_Cod_Unidad = '{0}') AND (OJDT.TransId NOT IN (SELECT L.U_NoAsient FROM [@SCGD_GRLINES] AS L WITH (nolock) INNER JOIN [@SCGD_GOODRECEIVE] AS GR WITH (nolock) ON GR.DocEntry = L.DocEntry AND GR.U_Unidad = '{0}' AND L.U_NoAsient IS NOT NULL)) AND (OJDT.RefDate <= '{4}') AND (JDT1.U_SCGD_Cod_Tran IN (SELECT Code FROM [@SCGD_TRAN_COMP] AS [@SCGD_TRAN_COMP_1])) AND (JDT1.Credit <> 0)
Union all SELECT count(1) FROM PCH1 WITH (nolock) INNER JOIN OPCH WITH (nolock) ON PCH1.DocEntry = OPCH.DocEntry INNER JOIN OJDT WITH (nolock) ON OPCH.TransId = OJDT.TransId WHERE (PCH1.U_SCGD_Cod_Unid = '{0}') AND (OPCH.DocType = '{5}' OR OPCH.DocType = '{6}') AND (OJDT.TransId NOT IN (SELECT L.U_NoAsient FROM [@SCGD_GRLINES] AS L WITH (nolock) INNER JOIN [@SCGD_GOODRECEIVE] AS GR WITH (nolock) ON GR.DocEntry = L.DocEntry AND GR.U_Unidad = '{0}' AND L.U_NoAsient IS NOT NULL)) AND (OPCH.DocDate <= '{4}') AND (PCH1.U_SCGD_Cod_Tran IN (SELECT Code FROM [@SCGD_TRAN_COMP] AS [@SCGD_TRAN_COMP_1])) Union all SELECT count(1) FROM RPC1 WITH (nolock) INNER JOIN ORPC WITH (nolock) ON RPC1.DocEntry = ORPC.DocEntry AND RPC1.TrgetEntry IS NULL INNER JOIN OJDT WITH (nolock) ON ORPC.TransId = OJDT.TransId WHERE (RPC1.U_SCGD_Cod_Unid = '{0}') AND (ORPC.DocType = '{5}' OR ORPC.DocType = '{6}') AND (OJDT.TransId NOT IN (SELECT L.U_NoAsient FROM [@SCGD_GRLINES] AS L WITH (nolock) INNER JOIN [@SCGD_GOODRECEIVE] AS GR WITH (nolock) ON GR.DocEntry = L.DocEntry AND GR.U_Unidad = '{0}' AND L.U_NoAsient IS NOT NULL)) AND (ORPC.DocDate <= '{4}') AND (RPC1.U_SCGD_Cod_Tran IN (SELECT Code FROM [@SCGD_TRAN_COMP] AS [@SCGD_TRAN_COMP_1])) Union all Select Count(1) from INV1 with (nolock) inner join OINV with (nolock) on INV1.DocEntry = OINV.DocEntry and TrgetEntry is null inner join OJDT with (nolock) on OINV.TransID = OJDT.TransId where OINV.U_SCGD_Cod_Unidad = '{0}' and OINV.DocType = 'S' and OJDT.TransID not in (Select U_NoAsient from dbo.[@SCGD_GRLINES] L with (nolock) inner join dbo.[@SCGD_GOODRECEIVE] GR with (nolock) on GR.DocEntry = L.DocEntry and GR.U_unidad = '{0}' and U_NoAsient is not null) and OINV.DocDate <= '{4}' UNION all SELECT Count(1) FROM OIGE with (nolock) INNER JOIN IGE1 with (nolock) ON IGE1.DocEntry = OIGE.DocEntry INNER JOIN OJDT with (nolock) ON OIGE.TransId = OJDT.TransId WHERE (OIGE.U_SCGD_Procesad = 1) AND (OIGE.U_SCGD_Cod_Unidad = '{0}') AND (OIGE.U_SCGD_Num_Vehiculo IS NOT NULL) AND (OJDT.RefDate <= '{4}') AND (OJDT.TransId NOT IN (SELECT L.U_NoAsient FROM [@SCGD_GRLINES] AS L with (nolock) INNER JOIN [@SCGD_GOODRECEIVE] AS GR with (nolock) ON GR.DocEntry = L.DocEntry AND GR.U_Unidad = '{0}' AND L.U_NoAsient IS NOT NULL)) GROUP BY OJDT.TransId, OIGE.DocEntry, OIGE.DocCur, OJDT.LocTotal, OIGE.VatSum, OIGE.DocNum, OIGE.DocTotal, OIGE.U_SCGD_Numero_OT, OIGE.SysRate, IGE1.AcctCode) as q
